title: Brady to the Bay? & Draft Talk with Matt Money Smith
itunes:title: Brady to the Bay? & Draft Talk with Matt Money Smith
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler are joined by Matt Money Smith to recap combine and all the "talk" that they heard going around between coaches and GMs. The guys chat about the upcoming draft class and Money breaks down who to really keep an eye out for. The heroes also break down the latest news including the Brady and SF rumors.
